{is_client}
&lt;p&gt;-Requires: lustre-backend-fs&lt;br/&gt;
-%endif&lt;br/&gt;
 Group: Development/Kernel&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt; %description modules&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
